reviewText: I don't usually watch movies that are this scary but will watch Michael Biehn in anything. He puts the "scary" in this scary movie. It's a must see for scary movie lovers.

THIS WAS GREAT FOR ME WAS MY 1ST EVER FILM APPERANCE AND IT HAD BEEN LOST, SO I WAS GLAD TO GET ANOTHER COPY. ALSO YOUR ARTIS IN HERE WITH ME JASON BATEMAN AND Michael Biehn AND ALSO Henry Thomas. GO OLD MOVIE TO WATCH.
